thread.title_full: Move over Calvin! Taylor Swift has an adorable new man in her life | The Advertiser

author: Erica Nasca
title: Move over Calvin! Taylor Swift has an adorable new man in her life |
text:
TAYLOR Swift looks like a complete natural in her new role as godmother. The 25-year-old pop star shared adorable snaps capturing the tender moment.
Taylor gazed at her new godson, with celebrity pal Jamie King by her side. “Meeting my boy” she captioned the shot. All smiles Jamie followed, “My loves meet. Baby boy Leo Thames and his God Mother = Bliss.”
Smitten godmother (Frame content direct link: https://www.instagram.com/p/5sfqjqDvBP/embed .)
Feeling clucky? A smitten Taylor Quote: d her song Never Grow Up on meeting little Leo, “Your little hand’s wrapped around my finger and it’s so quiet in the world tonight...”
Tender touch (Frame content direct link: https://www.instagram.com/p/5sfv0_jvBe/embed .)
Hart of Dixie star Jamie King made the announcement on Instagram earlier this year, “@taylorswift will forever be looking over our new baby” and then welcomed her second child to the world on July 16. She spoke about her faith in Taylor early on, expressing gratitude on Instagram after the singer caught a red-eye flight during her 1989 world tour to throw the ultimate star-studded baby shower.
Baby shower (Frame content direct link: https://www.instagram.com/p/37SHmsjvAq/embed .)
“How can I put this into words... @taylorswift is not only going to be an exquisite Godmother but one of the best friends one could ask for. Thank you Tay for throwing me such an insanely beautiful baby shower. Less then 12 hours after performing for 100k strong. I love you SO MUCH xx,” said a proud Jaime.
Chosen one (Frame content direct link: https://www.instagram.com/p/ztsEbJDvOu/embed .)
Taylor’s beau Calvin Harris will have to make room for her new little man in her already busy schedule. Speaking to a New York radio station this month, Harris said he was “insanely happy” in his relationship with the I Knew You Were Trouble singer. “It’s going absolutely fantastic,” Harris said.
‘Insanely happy’ ... The loved-up couple on July 4 long weekend. Picture: Instagram Source: Supplied
‘Forever looking over him’ ... The star was chuffed to meet Leo. Picture: AAP Source: AP
Swift’s new role may prompt the next step for the infatuated celebrity couple. Calvin shared his first photo of Swift with his 3.3 million followers on Instagram earlier this month, in which the singer is grilling vegetables above the caption, “She cooks too.”
Ticks the boxes (Frame content direct link: https://www.instagram.com/p/4qP-3tN3PK/embed .)
